OOC: I don't know who Shadow Warrior is or if he's even still in the 
rpg, but if he reads this just remember, I couldn't just let the puppy 
die.

BIC:  As the last of Cutie's energy drains as his spark is pierced his 
subconcious takes over.  It psycically travels to a warrior of great 
potential, yet unreconized, Eyebright.

Cutie's subconcious: Eyebright.  I will be gone soon.  We can help 
each other.  I will give you what energy I have left to keep you alive 
until help can arrive for you, but someday, by accepting this gift you 
make a pact that you shall avenge me (this isn't illegal is it).  TAKE 
IT!

He wills his energy into the pup.

OOC: So does the pup accept.  He'd be stupid not to.  He'll be able to 
transform won't he?
